ecially those not in linkage disequilibrium with SNPs) may have contributed disproportionately to human diversity and selection.','Probe signal intensity,Probe signal intensity','Agilent Genomic Workbench ADM2 algorithm,Agilent Genomic Workbench ADM2 algorithm','Oligo aCGH,Oligo aCGH','Agilent Eichler Human CNP 180K v2.1,Agilent Eichler Human CNP 180K v3.0','GRCh37,GRCh37.p13,GRCh38,GRCh38.p2,NCBI36','GCA_000001405.14,GCA_000001405.15,GCA_000001405.17,GCF_000001405.12,GCF_000001405.13,GCF_000001405.28');
